<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433815>
    dc:description "FIGURES 80–83. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, distinctive characters. (Position of antennal insertions): 80. Dorsal (Choraginae). 81, Lateral (Anthribinae). (Lateral carina of prothorax): 82, Complete. 83, Incomplete. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433815/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433811>
    dc:description "FIGURES 75–79. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, lateral habitus. (Tribe Stenocerini) 75, Stenocerus angulicollis Jekel. 76, Stenocerus longulus Jekel. 77, Stenocerus frontalis Gyllenhal. (Tribe Zygaenodini) 78, Ormiscus sp. (Tribe Araecerini) 79, Araecerus fasciculatus DeGeer. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433811/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433817>
    dc:description "FIGURES 84–87. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, distinctive characters. 84, Antennal club 3-articulate. 85, Mesial sinus in rostrum (Eugonus sp.). 86, Antennal insertion foveiform (Corrhecerus sp.). 87, Antennal insertion sulciform (Phaenithon sp.). Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433774>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–14. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, lateral habitus. (Tribe Basitropini) 9, Eugonus subcylindricus Fahraeus. 10, Phaenithon albosparsus Labram & Imhoff. 11, Phaenithon curvipes (Germar). 12, Phaenithon discifer Jordan. 13, Phaenithon jucundus Jordan. 14, Phaenithon perfectus Jordan. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433774/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433776>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–19. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Corrhecerini) 15, Corrhecerus hector Jekel. 16, Nemotrichus dorsomaculatus Jekel. (Tribe Cratoparini) 17, Euparius ajax (Jekel). 18, Euparius clitelliger Fahraeus. 19, Euparius stratus Jordan. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433776/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433780>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–24. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, lateral habitus. (Tribe Corrhecerini) 20, Corrhecerus hector Jekel. 21, Nemotrichus dorsomaculatus Jekel. (Tribe Cratoparini) 22, Euparius ajax (Jekel). 23, Euparius clitelliger Fahraeus. 24, Euparius stratus Jordan. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433770>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–8. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Basitropini) 3, Eugonus subcylindricus Fahraeus. 4, Phaenithon albosparsus Labram & Imhoff. 5, Phaenithon curvipes (Germar). 6, Phaenithon discifer Jordan.7, Phaenithon jucundus Jordan. 8, Phaenithon perfectus Jordan. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433809>
    dc:description "FIGURES 70–74. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Stenocerini) 70, Stenocerus angulicollis Jekel. 71, Stenocerus longulus Jekel. 72, Stenocerus frontalis Gyllenhal. (Tribe Zygaenodini) 73, Ormiscus sp. (Tribe Araecerini) 74, Araecerus fasciculatus DeGeer. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433809/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433803>
    dc:description "FIGURES 59–64. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Platyrhinini) 59, Strabus niger (Jordan). 60, Homocloeus pardalis Jordan. (Tribe Platystomini) 61, Toxonotus pistor Jordan. (Tribe Ptychoderini) 62, Ptychoderes brevis Jordan. 63, Ptychoderes jordani Frieser. 64, Ptychoderes rugicollis Jordan. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433803/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433805>
    dc:description "FIGURES 65–69. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, lateral habitus. (Tribe Platyrhinini) 65, Strabus niger (Jordan). 66, Homocloeus pardalis Jordan. (Tribe Platystomini) 67, Toxonotus pistor Jordan. (Tribe Ptychoderini) 68, Ptychoderes brevis Jordan. 69, Ptychoderes jordani Frieser. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433805/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433793>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41–45. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Ischnocerini) 41, Meconemus tuberculatus Labram & Imhoff. 42, Meconemus metallicus (Jordan). (Tribe Piesocorynini) 43, Brevibarra scotosagis Jordan. 44, Lagopezus morio Jordan. 45, Lagopezus tenuicornis (Fabricius). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433797>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46–50. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, lateral habitus. (Tribe Ischnocerini) 46, Meconemus tuberculatus Labram & Imhoff. 47, Meconemus metallicus (Jordan). (Tribe Piesocorynini) 48, Brevibarra scotosagis Jordan. 49, Lagopezus morio Jordan. 50, Lagopezus tenuicornis (Fabricius). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433799>
    dc:description "FIGURES 51–54. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, dorsal habitus. (Tribe Piesocorynini) 51, Piesocorynus brevis (Jordan). 52, Piesocorynus homoeus (Jordan). 53, Piesocorynus plagifer (Jordan). 54, Piesocorynus tristis (Jekel). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433799/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4433819>
    dc:description "FIGURES 88–93. Species of Anthribidae recorded from Panama, distinctive characters. 88, Scutellum below basal margin of elytra (Gymnognathini). 89, Scutellum above basal margin of elytra. 90, Eyes oblique, upper margin sinuous (Domoptolis. sp.). 91, Eyes parallel, rounded (Gymnognathus sp.). 92, Postbasal carina (Anthiera sp.). 93, Front tibia with brush-like lobe (Anthiera sp.). Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4433819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

